# 🇬🇷 ShuddhiCheck AI – Phase II: Greece Readiness

This folder includes the official readiness brief and strategic rollout plan for ShuddhiCheck AI’s Phase II expansion into Greece.

📌 **Key Highlights**
- Alignment with EU AI Act and GDPR
- Compliance oversight by the Hellenic Data Protection Authority (HDPA)
- Supported by national eHealth frameworks (NeHIF, Elevate Greece)
- Bilingual support (Modern Greek + English) enabled for health system partners

📄 [Download Greece Readiness Brief (PDF)](./ShuddhiCheckAI_PhaseII_Greece_Readiness.pdf)

---

## 🏛️ National & Regional Health Governance

- 🏥 **EOPYY** – National Organization for the Provision of Health Services
- 🏛 **Ministry of Health – Greece** – National regulatory authority
- 🧠 **HDPA** – GDPR and AI governance body
- 🌐 **Ministry of Digital Governance** – Public sector AI policy coordination
- 🧬 **HDHC** – Hellenic Digital Health Cluster

---

## 🌐 Language & Localization Strategy

| Language        | Status           |
|------------------|------------------|
| **Modern Greek** | ✅ Official & required for public rollout |
| **English**       | ✅ Widely used in digital health and innovation sectors |
| **Bilingual Support** | ✅ Recommended for outreach, demos, and stakeholder materials |

ShuddhiCheck AI supports bilingual platform adaptation (Modern Greek + English) for maximum accessibility in Greece’s healthcare system.

---

## 🛠️ Next Steps

- Upload the PDF brief to this folder
- Begin outreach to HDPA and the Ministry of Digital Governance
- Localize dashboard mockups and compliance features for Greek stakeholders
